   <dc:title>Handwritten letter from Schenker to F. A. Schmidt (Beethoven-Haus), dated November 27,
    1913</dc:title>

   <dcterms:created>1913-11-27T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
   <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2019-09-06</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
   <dc:description>Schenker asks the Beethoven-Haus to prepare and supply him with photographs of
    the autograph manuscript of the first movement of Beethoven's Piano Sonata in C minor, Op. 111,
    and announces the publication of his Erläuterungsausgabe of Op. 109 and monograph on Beethoven's
    Ninth Symphony.</dc:description>
   <dc:subject>Autograph; Ausgabe; edition; Satz; movement; photographieren; to photograph; weiss
    auf schwarz; white-on-black; Aufnahme; picture; Monographie; monograph; Erfolg;
    success</dc:subject>



